# Codebase Structure

```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── common/          # Shared (Navigation, ThemeToggle)
│   ├── contexts/        # React context providers (ThemeContext)
│   ├── screens/        # Route-level screens by feature
│   │   ├── admin/      # Admin scripts (AdminUserManagement, etc.)
│   │   ├── auth/       # Login, Register, Profile, Settings
│   │   ├── budget/     # Budget tool scripts
│   │   ├── calculator/ # Investment calculator
│   │   ├── financeQuest/
│   │   ├── lifebalance/
│   │   ├── quiz/
│   │   └── adult/
│   ├── ui/             # Radix-based primitives (button, card, input, etc.)
│   └── widgets/        # Reusable widgets (modals, InvestmentCalculator)
├── firebase/            # initFirebase, auth
├── hooks/               # Custom hooks (useAnalytics, useToolConfig)
├── lib/                 # Utilities (utils, userUtils, toolConfig)
├── services/            # External services (seoService)
└── utils/               # Build/script utils (generateSitemap)
```

## Organisation Rules
- **Screens**: One folder per feature; `scripts/` subfolder for multi-file features
- **Components**: Use `@/` path alias for imports
- **Firebase**: Centralised in `firebase/`; never initialise Firebase elsewhere
